image_analysis.description: A photograph showing a row of heavy winter coats hanging on a metal rack inside a closet or room with wood-paneled walls. The coats include several parkas with fur-trimmed hoods. One prominent red parka features a Canada Goose logo patch on the sleeve. Other coats are in colors such as white, tan, and dark blue/black. Above the rack, there is a small wooden shelf holding a clear acrylic box containing various small items like brushes. The walls are made of horizontal cedar-like wood planks.
image_analysis.layout: The image is a full-frame photograph with a document reference number at the bottom right corner.
